<L>__{interior entrance hall, karenin house, same}
<D>__{time day}
<A>__{kapitonich, pulling on his livery greatcoat, comes to the inner glass door and lets anna in. he does not recognise her.}
<C>__{anna}
<D>__{i have brought something for sergei alexeyich.}
<A>__{kapitonich scrutinises her, prepared to forestall her.}
<C>__{kapitonich}
<D>__{he is not up yet. would you wish to wait? who shall i say . . . ?}
<A>__{kapitonich peers at her and realises who she is. he steps back and bows.}
<C>__{kapitonich }
<D>__{please come in, your excellency.}
<A>__{anna goes quickly to the stairs.}
<C>__{kapitonich }
<D>__{allow me to announce you. the tutor may be there and not dressed.}
<A>__{anna shakes her head and is almost running away from him. kapitonich gives chase.}
